Author: goat, modded by Franz
Name: Dalamud.DiscordBridge
Punchline: Receive your chat messages via Discord.
Description: This plugin allows you to receive your chat messages via Discord.
Changelog:
Removes any invalid chat types a user might've had when loading config. While this should normally be impossible, Franz messed something up previously and some people may have added no-longer-valid types. This just purges them while keeping the rest of the config. Sorry!

On the flip side, it also fixes the plugin from completely failing for those users. any removed invalid types will be in your Dalamud log in case you're curious.
